    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/9d00eb284359ccf52386f37bfea1373c.poster.avif?t=1772377017\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/9d00eb284359ccf52386f37bfea1373c.webm?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/9d00eb284359ccf52386f37bfea1373c.mp4?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Corbel is a 3rd person medieval city builder with a big difference. Play as a giant and command tiny villagers to gather resources, transport goods, grow food, defend, and help you build. Manage production lines so you can keep expanding. Build this micro kingdom into a vast city while defending it from waves of gnome attacks or at your own pace in peaceful mode.    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tower over the buildings you create</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/d7f4f932f271b8626ed606d124622130.poster.avif?t=1772377017\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/d7f4f932f271b8626ed606d124622130.webm?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/d7f4f932f271b8626ed606d124622130.mp4?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A giant in a tiny world. Take part in construction, build dozens of different buildings piece by piece to grow your kingdom and strengthen your crown. You are the ruler here, expand your city at your own pace and decide its destiny, or kick a building down and start again.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Command your villagers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/d7c25222af0f61e01eabe5c0fa148c0b.poster.avif?t=1772377017\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/d7c25222af0f61e01eabe5c0fa148c0b.webm?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/d7c25222af0f61e01eabe5c0fa148c0b.mp4?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These villagers can't do it alone, pick them up and give them tasks, from mining rock to growing crops. Assign followers to carry extra building parts, transport resources, and even help defend. They will do anything you tell them, but without guidance they are doomed. Build production chains staffed by your villagers to allow you to build your city. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Defend against hordes of enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/c8e0b78b42ddf2c909e567d1e10ebd50.poster.avif?t=1772377017\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/c8e0b78b42ddf2c909e567d1e10ebd50.webm?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/c8e0b78b42ddf2c909e567d1e10ebd50.mp4?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the fight yourself, use a range of weapons to keep your creations and villagers safe from huge hordes of pillaging gnomes. Build towers and fortifications to assist in the defence of your kingdom. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Be the best ruler in all the land</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/c091ba784306ce33d269aa8392bd7519.poster.avif?t=1772377017\" width=1170 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/c091ba784306ce33d269aa8392bd7519.webm?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005270/extras/c091ba784306ce33d269aa8392bd7519.mp4?t=1772377017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the giant you can do everything better than any single villager, mine, craft, and transport resources yourself. Pick your ruler and craft the kindom to be your own. Play through the story mode and stop the gnomes from ever causing trouble again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
